{
  "texts": [
    "DDIs were considered either clinically significant or clinically unimportant from a panel of 3 clinical pharmacists.",
    "The medication regimens, patient cases, and explanations on the DDIs are included in the supplemental material.",
    "This study included two phases: 1) evaluating ChatGPT (GPT-4) to identify DDI interactions from a medication regimen in a fashion similar to a drug-interaction database, 2) evaluating ChatGPT (GPT-4) to identify DDI interactions and provide clinical recommendations from a patient case.",
    "The primary outcome was if GPT-4 identified the most relevant DDI within the medication regimen.",
    "Secondary outcomes included evaluating GPT-4's interaction rationale, clinical relevance ranking, and overall clinical recommendation."
  ]
}